(70, 85, 0, 35, 'Matt Putty/Matt Granite/Matt Bathroom Tiles'),
(71, 75, 0, 36, 'Drawing inspiration from the opulent Grosvenor House Hotel in London, the Grosvenor™ tile range is imbued with the same timeless styling and luxurious aesthetic. Use these rectangular border tiles with coordinating corner and central tiles to give your individual tile arrangement the perfect finishing touch.\n\nSuitable for use with underfloor heating providing the correct substrate preparation and a suitable flexible cement based tile adhesive and grouts are used. For more information on fitting please visit our knowledge base or contact your local store.\nProduct Code: 630370\nProduct Colour:Black, White\nTile Surface: Floor, Wall\nTile Size: 33cm x 11cm Rectangular\nTile Depth (cm): 0.83'),
