(93, 75, 0, 46, 'A tumbled finish gives these modular travertine tiles an unpolished and textured look. Quarried in the Afyon region of Turkey, this natural stone is sought after for its elegant silver grey hues. The swirling patterns of silver, cream, fawn and gold across the surface vary from piece to piece and will add a unique look to your space. Lay these large tiles out before fixing to achieve a stunning blend of colours across the entire area. \n\nSuitable for use with underfloor heating providing the correct substrate preparation and a suitable flexible cement based tile adhesive and grouts are used.\nProduct Code: 631084\nCoverage Per Box: 0.743m²\nTiles Per Box: 6\nProduct Colour: Grey\nTile Surface: Floor, Wall\nTile Size: 0.74m² Modular\nTile Depth (cm): 1.2'),
(94, 85, 0, 46, 'Aurelius Modular/Aurelius Tumbled / Aurelius Travertine /Aurelius Outdoor Tiles\n'),
(95, 75, 0, 47, 'The rectangular Aurelius™ polished travertine tile – sourced from Turkey\'s Afyon region – has a distinctive spirit. It\'s characterised by an alluring swirl of gold and cream hues offset by a chic silver and grey background. As each of these medium sized gloss tiles is crafted from natural stone, the patterns and tones will vary. Lay them out before fixing into place to ensure the colours coordinate perfectly for a flawless effect. \n\nSuitable for use with underfloor heating providing the correct substrate preparation and a suitable flexible cement based tile adhesive and grouts are used.\nProduct Code: 631096\nProduct Colour: Grey\nTile Surface: Floor, Wall\nTile Size: 61cm x 30.5cm Rectangular\nTile Depth (cm): 1.2'),
(96, 85, 0, 47, 'Aurelius Polished /Aurelius Travertine /Aurelius Outdoor Tiles'),
(97, 75, 0, 48, 'Cut from a quarry in Turkey\'s Afyon province, the Aurelius™ large tumbled travertine tile will lend a distinctive finish to your living space. Each rectangular piece features swirling golds and creams on a chic light grey and silver background. As these distinctive unpolished tiles are crafted from textured natural stone, their hues and patterns will vary. Lay them out ahead of fixing to achieve a beautifully coordinated effect.\n\nSuitable for use with underfloor heating providing the correct substrate preparation and a suitable flexible cement based tile adhesive and grouts are used.\nProduct Code: 631081\nProduct Colour: Grey\nTile Surface: Floor, Wall\nTile Size: 61cm x 40.6cm Rectangular\nTile Depth (cm): 1.2'),
(98, 85, 0, 48, 'Aurelius Tumbled /Aurelius Travertine /Aurelius Outdoor Tiles'),
(99, 75, 0, 49, 'These rectangular Aurelius™ honed travertine tiles are enlivened by an appealing array of colours. Their matt surfaces feature creams and golds in exquisite swirling patterns on an elegant base of light grey and silver. These medium sized tiles are crafted from unpolished natural stone quarried in the Afyon region of Turkey. Lay them out before fixing to harmonise shades across the entire area.\nProduct Code: 631090\nProduct Colour: Grey\nTile Surface: Floor, Wall\nTile Size: 61cm x 30.5cm Rectangular\nTile Depth (cm): 1.2'),
(100, 85, 0, 49, 'Aurelius Honed /Aurelius Travertine /Aurelius Outdoor Tiles'),
(101, 75, 0, 50, 'Choose these rectangular Sandelwood Honed & Filled travertine tiles to give your interior an attractive contemporary look. The design blends light cream and ivory tones that feel tranquil and sophisticated. These unpolished, textured tiles are crafted from natural stone and feature fine linear veins running throughout. Due to the way the product is made, you\'ll see beautiful natural variations in colour and pattern. Each tile is carefully selected to ensure as much consistency in colour as possible and to avoid imperfections. It\'s a good idea to lay out these tiles before fixing to ensure you\'re happy with the mix of tones. Please note, these tiles can be used indoors but are not suitable for wet rooms or outdoors.\nProduct Code: 631065\nProduct Colour: Beige\nTile Surface: Floor, Wall\nTile Size: 61cm x 30.5cm Rectangular\nTile Depth (cm): 1.2\n'),
